---
title: Mexican Chilli Bowl with Mixed Beans and Crispy Tortilla Strips
description: You'll have some tortillas left over after today's recipe. Why not try making your own tortilla chips? Use the same method as the strips here but cut them into triangles instead and add any spices you fancy. Or what about trying sweet tortilla chips? Use sugar and a sprinkle of cinnamon to create a Mexican-inspired dessert!
